translate spanish newcoo_10_05de472f:

    # narrador "You unfold the newspaper and begin to read aloud."
    narrador "Despliegas el periódico y comienzas a leer en voz alta."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:10
translate spanish newcoo_10_f44f0a74:

    # player "Elegia, the island of music, will open its doors to tourists from all over the world in the coming days."
    player "Elegia, la isla de la música, abrirá sus puertas a turistas de todo el mundo en los próximos días."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:11
translate spanish newcoo_10_0cdf0272:

    # player "Known for its music academies, cutting-edge technology, and top-level professionals, many young people travel there to study singing, instruments, and composition."
    player "Conocida por sus academias de música, tecnología de punta y profesionales de primer nivel, muchos jóvenes viajan allí para estudiar canto, instrumentos y composición."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:12
translate spanish newcoo_10_79f759b8:

    # player "This year, several world-class musical prodigies are expected to debut on the various stages of this great city..."
    player "Este año se espera que varios prodigios musicales de talla mundial debuten en los distintos escenarios de esta gran ciudad..."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:13
translate spanish newcoo_10_7aba7935:

    # player "(Musicians!!... any respectable crew needs to have one...)"
    player "(¡Músicos!... cualquier equipo respetable necesita tener uno...)"

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:14
translate spanish newcoo_10_a318adc9:

    # player "(Hmm... with some luck, maybe there'll be a sexy singer I can charm into joining my crew...)"
    player "(Hmm... con un poco de suerte, tal vez haya una cantante sexy a la que pueda convencer para que se una a mi equipo...)"

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:20
translate spanish newcoo_10_c54cf9e1:

    # robin "Elegia... i've read about it. the musical culture of that island is quite advanced, they even have orchestras using unique instruments from the new world."
    robin "Elegia... he leído sobre ello. La cultura musical de esa isla es bastante avanzada, incluso tienen orquestas que utilizan instrumentos únicos del nuevo mundo."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:21
translate spanish newcoo_10_18fe7b5a:

    # robin "It's a culturally significant island for the world government... If i'm not mistaken, it's either a summer or spring island."
    robin "Es una isla culturalmente significativa para el gobierno mundial... Si no me equivoco, es una isla de verano o de primavera."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:27
translate spanish newcoo_10_9e385794:

    # nami "It's an island that's a bit far from here... But i saw some eternal poses for sale in this city, it might be interesting to head there..."
    nami "Es una isla que está un poco lejos de aquí... Pero vi algunas poses eternas en venta en esta ciudad, podría ser interesante ir allí..."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:28
translate spanish newcoo_10_396164fb:

    # nami "But... Why the sudden interest, captain? Don't tell me that..."
    nami "Pero... ¿Por qué el repentino interés, capitán? No me diga que..."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:30
translate spanish newcoo_10_ff9cc7d8:

    # player "(Damn it, she figured it out so fast!)"
    player "(¡Maldita sea, lo descubrió tan rápido!)"

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:31
translate spanish newcoo_10_09e4b3ba:

    # player "F-for the culture! yes! culture and... tourism. It'd be good for the crew to relax a bit after these days of hard work."
    player "¡Por la cultura! ¡Sí! Cultura y... turismo. Le vendría bien a la tripulación relajarse un poco después de estos días de duro trabajo."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:34
translate spanish newcoo_10_731616fa:

    # nami "Haha... sure. whatever you say"
    nami "Jaja... claro. Lo que tú digas."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:36
translate spanish newcoo_10_2e52efc4:

    # nami "If we're really going to visit Elegia, we'll need to buy the eternal pose i mentioned... That should be the first step, then i'll handle the rest"
    nami "Si realmente vamos a visitar Elegia, necesitaremos comprar la pose eterna que mencioné... Ese debería ser el primer paso, luego me encargaré del resto."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:38
translate spanish newcoo_10_04f202ac:

    # robin "It could be an interesting stop. Besides, it's not every day an island like that opens to the general public."
    robin "Podría ser una parada interesante. Además, no todos los días una isla como esa abre sus puertas al público."

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:40
translate spanish newcoo_10_67921517:

    # player "(Yes! having a sexy singer on board would be amazing!)"
    player "(¡Sí! ¡Tener una cantante sexy a bordo sería increíble!)"

# game/scripts/Events/Player/newscoo.rpy:41
translate spanish newcoo_10_cf73b876:

    # player "Alright! let's go buy the eternal pose and set sail!"
    player "¡Muy bien! ¡Vamos a comprar la pose eterna y zarpar!"

